task:
Attached are AtlasXomics fragments and peaks files for a spatial single-cell ATAC-seq project. Calculate the FRiP (Fraction of Reads in Peaks) metric and perform filtering. Return the 10th percentile (p10) FRiP value on the filtered cells. Return EXACTLY in the following format:
<EVAL_ANSWER>
{
  "p10_frip": <float>
}
</EVAL_ANSWER>
